"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"vehemently,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of waves, and of a torrent, (K, TA,) and of a sea: (TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a great torrent:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"abundance and vehemence"},{"kind":"text","text":"of water: (L:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a great quantity of water"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a torrent: and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a great number"},{"kind":"text","text":"of people. (AA.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaA='a duf~aAEN mina Alr~ijaAli waAln~isaA='i","text_ar":"جَا=ءَ دُفَّاعٌ مِنَ الرِّجَالِ وَالنِّسَا=ءِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"There came a great number of men and women crowding one upon another."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b2-  Also (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A great thing by which a similar great thing is impelled, propelled,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"repelled."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, * TA.)"}],"source_refs":["K","TA","S","L"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}